      • bind

        public static TypeDescription.Generic.Visitor<TypeDescription.Generic> bind(TypeDescription.Generic typeDescription)
        Creates a visitor that binds the variables of the given generic type by the generic type's values. If the provided type represents a raw generic type or if the generic type is incomplete, the returned visitor erases all found type variables instead.
        Parameters:
        typeDescription - The type description to be bound.
        Returns:
        A visitor that binds any type variables
